Create a calculator springboot microservice from spring.io
spring-boot-calculator

Create Controller class Calculate

@RestController
public class Calculate{

@Getmapping(/add)
public float addition(){
     return 5;
}

@Getmapping(/sub)
public float subtraction(){
   return 3;
}
@Getmapping(/mul)
public float multiplication(){
 return 12
}
@Getmapping(/div)
public float division(){

return 4;
}

test it with browser
test with postman
test with curl


Marks: 5marks

